channel.title: Thanx god it works
channel.description:
I know its an useless post, I know I might be flamed but...
I was having fun in mopar, like a lot of ppl...
Then, while trying to install jdk and jre, everything fucked up.
First error : Java could not be identified as an internal or external command
While reinstalling jdk and jre
Second error :
Error 1772. One of the windows installer processes didnt end as expected. Please contact your system vendor.
Naturally, couldn't install them I finnaly installed em(after 2 hours of googling)...but I got this
Error in the initialization of UM
So I completely unistalled windows installer, wich made almost all my apps stop working (im still reinstalling some of them)
Now I reinstall JRE with JDK (online installation)... The installation worked.
I open my moparscape file, I get an error, try re-downloading it...but I realise after it was just a common crash.
Now it works. After two days of fighting with my computer :P
